featured_reviews.review_id: I loved this mosque. Due to cold the whole flooring is carpeted.While you visit MG marg please make some time to offer namaz. It will be a different experience. Doing wudu in with the cold freezing water and doing namaz after that will warm your body. It's just beside mg marg. You can follow google map to go there.Its just beside rumtek taxi stand.
